42
00:06:42,153 --> 00:06:43,488
{\fnSimHei}埃利斯{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Ellis.{\r}

43
00:06:44,906 --> 00:06:48,826
{\fnSimHei}罗杰 有时候也叫做小罗{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Roger. Sometime they call him Lil Raj.{\r}

44
00:06:50,203 --> 00:06:52,413
{\fnSimHei}他们都曾是卡鲁肯农场的监工{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}They was overseers at the Carrucan plantation.{\r}

