60
00:07:37,583 --> 00:07:39,460
{\fnSimHei}再给你一次机会 娘炮{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Last chance, fancy pants.{\r}

61
00:07:40,878 --> 00:07:43,214
{\fnSimHei}哦 好吧{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Oh, very well.{\r}

62
00:08:11,993 --> 00:08:14,412
{\fnSimHei}抱歉 射杀了你的牲口{\r}
