64
00:08:16,664 --> 00:08:18,958
{\fnSimHei}就冲动行事{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}before you had a moment to come to your senses.{\r}

65
00:08:19,125 --> 00:08:22,545
{\fnSimHei}你个狗娘养的!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You goddamn son of a bitch!{\r}

66
00:08:22,712 --> 00:08:25,506
{\fnSimHei}- 你杀了罗斯科!  - 好吧...{\r}
