{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Damn leg's busted!  - No doubt.{\r}

72
00:08:39,562 --> 00:08:42,106
{\fnSimHei}好了 请你尽量不要鬼哭狼嚎{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Now, if you could keep your caterwauling down to a minimum,{\r}

73
00:08:42,273 --> 00:08:45,610
{\fnSimHei}我想最后再问小姜戈几个问题{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I'd like to finish my line of inquiry with young Django.{\r}

74
00:08:49,614 --> 00:08:53,075
{\fnSimHei}- 天杀的我靠!  - 接着我刚说的...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- God-fuckin'-damn it!  - As I was saying...{\r}

75
00:08:53,242 --> 00:08:56,954
{\fnSimHei}要是你再看见布里托兄弟你能认出他们吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}if you were to see the Brittle Brothers again, you could recognize 'em?{\r}

76
00:08:57,622 --> 00:08:59,332
{\fnSimHei}能{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Yeah.{\r}

77
00:08:59,498 --> 00:09:00,791
{\fnSimHei}成交!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Sold American!{\r}

78
00:09:00,958 --> 00:09:04,921
{\fnSimHei}那 斯派克先生? 斯派克? 小姜戈要多少钱?{\r}
