{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Nigger! Don't you touch my brother's coat.{\r}

86
00:10:00,685 --> 00:10:05,606
{\fnSimHei}他妈的! 疼!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Goddamn it! Oh!{\r}

87
00:10:07,275 --> 00:10:12,446
{\fnSimHei}一百... 一十... 二十...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}One hundred... ten... 20...{\r}

88
00:10:12,613 --> 00:10:14,448
{\fnSimHei}五块...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}and five...{\r}

89
00:10:15,700 --> 00:10:16,867
{\fnSimHei}这是小姜戈的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}for young Django here.{\r}

90
00:10:17,034 --> 00:10:19,203
{\fnSimHei}既然你留着也没什么用{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}And since he won't be needing it anymore,{\r}

91
00:10:19,370 --> 00:10:21,872
{\fnSimHei}我想连你哥的老马一并买下{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I'd like to purchase your brother's nag.{\r}

92
00:10:22,581 --> 00:10:27,545
{\fnSimHei}还有 斯派克先生 我恐怕还需要一张卖身契{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Also, Mr. Speck, I'm afraid I will require a bill of sale.{\r}

93
00:10:27,712 --> 00:10:29,297
{\fnSimHei}你有吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Do you have one?{\r}

94
00:10:29,463 --> 00:10:32,383
{\fnSimHei}去死吧 牙医{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You go to hell, dentist.{\r}

95
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:34,552
{\fnSimHei}我猜就没有{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I thought not.{\r}

96
00:10:34,719 --> 00:10:38,222
{\fnSimHei}别担心 我是有备而来{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}No worries. I come prepared.{\r}

97
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:44,145
{\fnSimHei}谢谢{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Thank you.{\r}

98
00:10:44,312 --> 00:10:47,898
{\fnSimHei}就用这个当契约吧{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}This will serve nicely as a bill of sale.{\r}

99
00:11:00,244 --> 00:11:01,245
{\fnSimHei}吁{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Whoa.{\r}

100
00:11:05,416 --> 00:11:08,878
{\fnSimHei}至于你们这些可怜的小鬼{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Now, as to you poor devils.{\r}

101
00:11:09,045 --> 00:11:14,091
{\fnSimHei}如此 就我看来 该考虑下一步做什么了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}So, as I see it, when it comes to the subject of what to do next,{\r}

102
00:11:14,258 --> 00:11:17,094
{\fnSimHei}现在是各位做出选择的时候了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}you gentlemen have two choices.{\r}

103
00:11:17,261 --> 00:11:22,391
{\fnSimHei}一条路是 我走之后 你们把活的那个斯派克从那牲口身下拽出来{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}One: Once I'm gone, you could lift that beast off the remaining Speck,{\r}

104
00:11:22,558 --> 00:11:24,477
{\fnSimHei}然后把他抬到最近的小镇{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}then carry him to the nearest town.{\r}

105
00:11:24,643 --> 00:11:28,230
{\fnSimHei}就是说得往回走大概至少37英里{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Which would be at least 37 miles back the way you came.{\r}

106
00:11:28,397 --> 00:11:34,070
{\fnSimHei}第二条路 你们可以把镣铐解开 拿上那把枪{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Or two: You could unshackle yourselves, take that rifle,{\r}

107
00:11:34,236 --> 00:11:36,781
{\fnSimHei}照着他脑袋上来一枪 然后把他z的尸骨深埋{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}put a bullet in his head, bury the two of them deep,{\r}

108
00:11:36,947 --> 00:11:40,493
{\fnSimHei}然后找个更开化的地方扎根{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}and then make your way to a more enlightened area of this country.{\r}

109
00:11:41,577 --> 00:11:42,745
{\fnSimHei}供君选择{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Choice is yours.{\r}

110
00:11:42,912 --> 00:11:47,291
{\fnSimHei}对了 考虑到你们识星象的几率略低{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Oh, and on the off chance there are any astronomy aficionados amongst you,{\r}

111
00:11:47,458 --> 00:11:50,461
{\fnSimHei}北极星在那边{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}the North Star is that one.{\r}

112
00:11:51,921 --> 00:11:55,091
{\fnSimHei}拜拜啦{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Ta-ta.{\r}

113
00:12:09,897 --> 00:12:13,984
{\fnSimHei}等等 小伙子们 我们可以谈谈!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Now wait a minute, fellas. Let's talk about this!{\r}

114
00:12:17,613 --> 00:12:21,033
{\fnSimHei}你们得讲讲道理!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You gotta be reasonable in a situation like this!{\r}

115
00:12:22,493 --> 00:12:25,496
{\fnSimHei}我不是坏人 我只是本分地工作!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I'm not a bad guy. I'm just doin' my job!{\r}

116
00:12:25,663 --> 00:12:29,250
{\fnSimHei}蓝莓兄 我最后一个苹果不也给了你吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Blueberry, didn't I give you my last apple?{\r}

117
00:12:29,417 --> 00:12:32,378
{\fnSimHei}这样吧 孩子们 带我去埃尔帕索城看大夫{\r}
