138
00:15:00,359 --> 00:15:01,986
{\fnSimHei}哎{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Alas.{\r}

139
00:15:03,362 --> 00:15:05,906
{\fnSimHei}我们现在得自己动手了{\r}
