140
00:15:08,325 --> 00:15:10,077
{\fnSimHei}坐下吧 孩子{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Sit down, my boy.{\r}

141
00:15:19,753 --> 00:15:22,631
{\fnSimHei}你是哪门子的牙医?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}What kind of dentist are you?{\r}

142
00:15:23,465 --> 00:15:28,053
{\fnSimHei}别看那个小车 其实我有五年没出诊了{\r}
