145
00:15:46,155 --> 00:15:47,990
{\fnSimHei}你知道什么叫赏金猎人吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Do you know what a bounty hunter is?{\r}

146
00:15:48,699 --> 00:15:49,742
{\fnSimHei}不知道{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}No.{\r}

147
00:15:49,908 --> 00:15:51,118
{\fnSimHei}好吧...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Well...{\r}

148
00:15:52,745 --> 00:15:56,874
{\fnSimHei}就跟奴隶买卖一样 拿人命换钱{\r}
