235
00:21:47,182 --> 00:21:49,851
{\fnSimHei}出来吧{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Come ahead.{\r}

236
00:21:56,900 --> 00:21:58,151
{\fnSimHei}赤手空拳啦?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You unarmed?{\r}

237
00:21:58,318 --> 00:22:00,028
{\fnSimHei}是 我们都缴械了{\r}
