240
00:22:06,410 --> 00:22:08,745
{\fnSimHei}介绍刚刚发生的那场事故?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}as to the incident that just occurred?{\r}

241
00:22:10,080 --> 00:22:12,541
