250
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:42,446
{\fnSimHei}我也深知这是条令人不安的坏消息{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I'm aware this is probably disconcerting news.{\r}

251
00:22:42,612 --> 00:22:45,782
{\fnSimHei}我敢打赌这个人是在大概两年前{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}But I'm willing to wager this man was elected sheriff{\r}

252
00:22:45,949 --> 00:22:48,452
