{\fnSimHei}巡回法院亨利・亚伦・罗德缪法官签发的逮捕证{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Circuit Court Judge Henry Allen Laudermilk of Austin, Texas.{\r}

258
00:23:07,554 --> 00:23:09,264
{\fnSimHei}你可以给他发个电报{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You're encouraged to wire him.{\r}

259
00:23:09,431 --> 00:23:14,478
{\fnSimHei}他会证实我的说辞 揭开你已故的亲爱的警长的真面目{\r}
