00:53:00,762 --> 00:53:02,806
{\fnSimHei}比其他人强多了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}That's better than most of them get.{\r}

617
00:53:02,973 --> 00:53:05,267
{\fnSimHei}坏人不应该有这种好报{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Damn sight better than he deserves.{\r}

618
00:53:13,441 --> 00:53:14,776
{\fnSimHei}枪放下吧{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Put down the rifle.{\r}

619
00:53:17,779 --> 00:53:19,489
{\fnSimHei}别怕 我没生你的气{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Don't worry, I'm not mad at you.{\r}

620
00:53:20,282 --> 00:53:22,617
{\fnSimHei}我们拿出斯密・巴考尔的通缉令{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Let's take out Smitty Bacall's handbill.{\r}

621
00:53:26,580 --> 00:53:28,081
{\fnSimHei}大声读出来{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Read it aloud.{\r}

622
00:53:28,957 --> 00:53:30,750
{\fnSimHei}就当是今天的功课{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Consider that today's lesson.{\r}

623
00:53:33,169 --> 00:53:35,839
{\fnSimHei}通缉 无论死活{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Wanted. Dead or alive.{\r}

624
00:53:36,798 --> 00:53:40,719
{\fnSimHei}斯密・巴考尔以及斯密・巴考尔的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Smitty Bacall and the Smitty Bacall{\r}

625
00:53:40,886 --> 00:53:43,138
{\fnSimHei}- 团伙  - 团伙{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Gang.  - Gang.{\r}

626
00:53:43,305 --> 00:53:46,975
{\fnSimHei}因谋杀以及打劫...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}For murder and stagecoach...{\r}

627
00:53:48,393 --> 00:53:49,936
{\fnSimHei}驿站马车{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}robbery.{\r}

628
00:53:50,103 --> 00:53:52,898
{\fnSimHei}- 七 零 零 零...  - 七千{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Seven-zero-zero-zero...  - Seven thousand.{\r}

629
00:53:53,064 --> 00:53:54,399
{\fnSimHei}千{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Thousand.{\r}

630
00:53:54,566 --> 00:53:58,778
{\fnSimHei}悬赏七千美元捉拿斯密・巴考尔{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}$7,000 for Smitty Bacall.{\r}

631
00:53:58,945 --> 00:54:04,034
{\fnSimHei}一千五百美元捉拿他的每个...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}$1,500 for each of his...{\r}

632
00:54:04,200 --> 00:54:05,994
{\fnSimHei}团伙...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}gang...{\r}

633
00:54:07,037 --> 00:54:09,039
{\fnSimHei}- 成...  - 成员{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Mem...  - Members.{\r}

634
00:54:09,748 --> 00:54:14,377
{\fnSimHei}已知的斯密・巴考尔团伙成员于下:{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Known members of the Smitty Bacall Gang are as follas:{\r}

635
00:54:14,544 --> 00:54:16,296
{\fnSimHei}- 如下  - 如下{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Follows.  - Follows.{\r}

636
00:54:16,463 --> 00:54:20,175
{\fnSimHei}丹迪・迈克尔斯 杰拉尔德・纳什和...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Dandy Michaels, Gerald Nash and...{\r}

637
00:54:21,301 --> 00:54:23,219
{\fnSimHei}疯子克雷格・昆斯{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Crazy Craig Koons.{\r}

638
00:54:24,220 --> 00:54:26,473
{\fnSimHei}这才是斯密・巴考尔的真面目{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}That is who Smitty Bacall is.{\r}

639
00:54:26,640 --> 00:54:29,517
{\fnSimHei}他要是22岁开始老实经营农场{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}If Smitty Bacall wanted to start a farm at 22,{\r}

640
00:54:29,684 --> 00:54:31,645
{\fnSimHei}就不会被印在这上面了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}they would never have printed that.{\r}

641
00:54:32,354 --> 00:54:35,774
{\fnSimHei}可斯密・巴考尔想抢劫马车{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}But Smitty Bacall wanted to rob stagecoaches{\r}

642
00:54:35,941 --> 00:54:38,360
{\fnSimHei}为达目的他不惜杀人{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}and he didn't mind killing people to do it.{\r}

643
00:54:39,027 --> 00:54:42,364
{\fnSimHei}你想做我的工作来挣钱救你妻子吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Do you want to save your wife by doing what I do?{\r}

644
00:54:43,615 --> 00:54:45,075
{\fnSimHei}这就是我的工作{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}This is what I do.{\r}

645
00:54:45,241 --> 00:54:48,787
{\fnSimHei}我杀人 用尸体换赏金{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I kill people and sell their corpses for cash.{\r}

646
00:54:49,704 --> 00:54:53,500
{\fnSimHei}这具尸体值七千美元{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}This corpse is worth $7,000.{\r}

647
00:54:53,667 --> 00:54:55,877
{\fnSimHei}别婆婆妈妈了 朝他开枪{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Now quit your pussyfooting and shoot him.{\r}

648
00:55:06,012 --> 00:55:07,389
{\fnSimHei}爸爸?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Pa?{\r}

649
00:55:07,555 --> 00:55:08,890
{\fnSimHei}爸爸!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Pa!{\r}

650
00:55:17,357 --> 00:55:19,067
{\fnSimHei}拿着{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Here.{\r}

651
00:55:19,234 --> 00:55:21,319
{\fnSimHei}你得保管好这斯密・巴考尔的通缉令{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You need to keep this Smitty Bacall handbill.{\r}

652
00:55:21,486 --> 00:55:23,571
{\fnSimHei}- 为什么?  - 这是好运气{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Why?  - It's good luck.{\r}

653
00:55:23,738 --> 00:55:26,533
{\fnSimHei}要保存好第一份赏金通缉令{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You always keep the handbill of your first bounty.{\r}

654
00:56:14,456 --> 00:56:15,874
{\fnSimHei}非常准{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}That's accurate.{\r}

655
00:57:24,192 --> 00:57:27,320
{\fnSimHei}医生 姜戈 你们好啊?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Doctor, Django, how the hell are ya?{\r}

656
00:57:28,363 --> 00:57:30,532
{\fnSimHei}那些又是谁啊?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Who the hell-a you got there?{\r}

657
00:57:30,698 --> 00:57:32,659
{\fnSimHei}威尔逊劳团伙{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}The Wilson-Lowe Gang.{\r}

658
00:57:32,826 --> 00:57:35,829
{\fnSimHei}什么威尔逊劳团伙?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Who the hell is the Wilson-Lowe Gang?{\r}

659
00:57:36,538 --> 00:57:41,084
{\fnSimHei}坏蛋查克・威尔逊 更坏的鲍比・劳和三个随从{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Bad Chuck Wilson and meaner Bobby Lowe and three of their acolytes.{\r}

660
00:57:41,251 --> 00:57:44,879
{\fnSimHei}哦 就放这儿吧 他们也跑不了了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Huh. Well, just leave 'em out here, they ain't going nowhere.{\r}

661
00:57:45,046 --> 00:57:47,423
{\fnSimHei}你们别在雪里待着 进屋来{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Why don't you come in then out of the snowy snow{\r}

662
00:57:47,590 --> 00:57:49,425
{\fnSimHei}喝点咖啡{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}and get yourselves some coffee.{\r}

663
00:57:49,592 --> 00:57:52,137
{\fnSimHei}昨天有人过生日 剩了点蛋糕{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}We had a birthday yesterday. Got some cake.{\r}

664
00:57:52,303 --> 00:57:53,721
{\fnSimHei}相当不错的蛋糕{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Pretty good.{\r}

665
00:58:04,303 --> 00:58:07,721
{\fnSimHei}在一个寒冷但收获颇丰的冬天后{\r}

666
00:58:07,803 --> 00:58:10,721
{\fnSimHei}姜戈和舒尔茨医生双双下山 去往...{\r}

667
00:58:15,869 --> 00:58:18,204
{\fnSimHei}往前走!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Move along!{\r}

668
00:58:18,803 --> 00:58:21,721
{\fnSimHei}密西西比州{\r}

669
00:58:23,543 --> 00:58:25,628
{\fnSimHei}走啊 黑鬼!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Move it, boy!{\r}

670
00:58:27,172 --> 00:58:28,423
{\fnSimHei}跟上了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Keep movin'.{\r}

671
00:58:28,590 --> 00:58:30,550
{\fnSimHei}到那个拍卖台上去{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Get on up on that auction block.{\r}

672
00:58:32,093 --> 00:58:34,470
{\fnSimHei}别让泥土拖慢你们的步伐 继续前进{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Don't let that mud slow you down. Keep going.{\r}

673
00:58:50,904 --> 00:58:52,155
{\fnSimHei}继续前行!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Keep goin'!{\r}

674
00:58:54,616 --> 00:58:58,536
{\fnSimHei}"布隆希达・沙夫特 27岁{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}"Broomhilda Von Shaft. Age 27,{\r}

