{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Come on, now, boy! It's a fight to the death!{\r}

787
01:05:34,140 --> 01:05:37,226
{\fnSimHei}你到底要不要打败他?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You either hit him or are you ain't?{\r}

788
01:05:45,234 --> 01:05:48,321
{\fnSimHei}- 大块头弗雷德 加把劲!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Big Fred, come on!{\r}

789
01:05:48,487 --> 01:05:50,031
{\fnSimHei}把他转过来! 马上...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Turn him around! Now...{\r}

790
01:05:53,826 --> 01:05:58,164
{\fnSimHei}黑鬼 利用你的优势! 加把劲儿啊! 发挥你的强项!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Use your strength, boy! Come on, now! Use your strength!{\r}

791
01:06:00,249 --> 01:06:02,043
{\fnSimHei}就这样!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}There you go!{\r}

792
01:06:03,377 --> 01:06:05,838
{\fnSimHei}就是这样! 看看{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}There you go! Look at that.{\r}

793
01:06:06,922 --> 01:06:09,884
{\fnSimHei}看吧 我告诉你要更用力{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}See, I told you to put some more power in there.{\r}

794
01:06:10,051 --> 01:06:12,094
{\fnSimHei}按我说的做 黑鬼!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Do what I told you, boy!{\r}

795
01:06:12,261 --> 01:06:13,721
{\fnSimHei}就这样!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}There you go!{\r}

796
01:06:13,888 --> 01:06:16,182
{\fnSimHei}- 不!  - 照我说的来!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- No!  - Do what I told ya!{\r}

797
01:06:16,349 --> 01:06:19,393
{\fnSimHei}把他戳瞎 黑鬼! 戳瞎他!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Blind him black, boy! Blind him black!{\r}

798
01:06:21,812 --> 01:06:24,315
{\fnSimHei}哦 不 路易吉{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Oh, no, Luigi.{\r}

799
01:06:27,526 --> 01:06:31,447
{\fnSimHei}哇! 哦 哈哈!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Whoo! Whoo-hoo-hoo!{\r}

800
01:06:32,073 --> 01:06:33,240
{\fnSimHei}噢...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Oh...{\r}

801
01:06:43,793 --> 01:06:45,086
{\fnSimHei}把他了结{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Finish him.{\r}

802
01:06:49,382 --> 01:06:51,133
{\fnSimHei}继续啊 了结了他!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Go on, boy, finish him!{\r}

803
01:06:55,638 --> 01:06:57,348
{\fnSimHei}这就是他被叫作大块头弗雷德的原因{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}That's why they call him Big Fred.{\r}

804
01:06:57,515 --> 01:07:00,935
{\fnSimHei}- 花的每分钱都值得  - 好吧 路易吉再见{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Worth every penny.  - Well, arrivederci, Luigi.{\r}

805
01:07:01,102 --> 01:07:03,312
{\fnSimHei}现在上来吧 休息一下{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Come on up, now, boy. Get yourself a rest.{\r}

806
01:07:03,479 --> 01:07:06,482
{\fnSimHei}你做的很好 相当好{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You did a fine job. A real fine job.{\r}

807
01:07:07,108 --> 01:07:08,818
{\fnSimHei}默西迪丝{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Mercedes.{\r}

808
01:07:29,922 --> 01:07:31,132
{\fnSimHei}我要龙舌兰酒{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Tequila.{\r}

809
01:07:41,142 --> 01:07:42,643
{\fnSimHei}你叫什么名字?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}What's your name?{\r}

810
01:07:44,812 --> 01:07:46,313
{\fnSimHei}我叫姜戈{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Django.{\r}

811
01:07:48,733 --> 01:07:50,401
{\fnSimHei}你能拼写吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Can you spell it?{\r}

812
01:07:52,528 --> 01:07:56,574
{\fnSimHei}是D-J-A-N-G-O{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}D-J-A-N-G-O.{\r}

813
01:07:58,075 --> 01:07:59,577
{\fnSimHei}D不发音{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}The D is silent.{\r}

814
01:07:59,744 --> 01:08:01,328
{\fnSimHei}我知道了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I know.{\r}

815
01:08:09,295 --> 01:08:12,798
{\fnSimHei}莫吉先生 你来照看我的新男仆{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Mr. Moguy, want you to take care of my new boy here.{\r}

816
01:08:12,965 --> 01:08:14,675
{\fnSimHei}给他找个房间 带软床的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You find him a room with a soft bed,{\r}

817
01:08:14,842 --> 01:08:17,428
{\fnSimHei}再找个人好好伺候下他{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}then you bring him up a pony to lick his pole.{\r}

818
01:08:17,595 --> 01:08:20,347
{\fnSimHei}但你明早得准备到糖果农场 听清了吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}But you be ready to travel to Candyland tomorrow morning, now, ya hear?{\r}

819
01:08:20,514 --> 01:08:21,515
{\fnSimHei}听到了 先生坎迪{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Yessir, Monsieur Candie.{\r}

820
01:08:21,682 --> 01:08:25,561
{\fnSimHei}罗斯科 走之前给弗雷德一大瓶啤酒{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Before you go, Roscoe, get Fred here a tall beer.{\r}

821
01:08:29,398 --> 01:08:32,401
{\fnSimHei}好好享受 是你自己挣来的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You enjoy that, boy. You've earned it.{\r}

822
01:08:32,568 --> 01:08:33,861
{\fnSimHei}是的 先生{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Yessir.{\r}

823
01:08:43,370 --> 01:08:47,166
{\fnSimHei}- 黑人 你叫什么?  - 他名叫姜戈・弗里曼{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- What's your name, boy?  - His name is Django Freeman.{\r}

824
01:08:50,711 --> 01:08:52,338
{\fnSimHei}你从哪儿把他挖来的?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Where'd you dig him up?{\r}

825
01:08:52,505 --> 01:08:55,758
{\fnSimHei}一个偶然的机缘让我遇上了姜戈{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}A fortuitous turn of events brought Django and myself together.{\r}

826
01:08:57,468 --> 01:08:59,553
{\fnSimHei}我听说过你{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I've heard tell about you.{\r}

827
01:09:00,304 --> 01:09:03,057
{\fnSimHei}我听说你四处散布说曼丁哥人不太强{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I heard you been telling everybody them Mandingos ain't no damn good.{\r}

828
01:09:03,224 --> 01:09:05,351
{\fnSimHei}大家卖的根本不值钱{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Ain't nothin' nobody is sellin' is worth buyin'.{\r}

829
01:09:05,518 --> 01:09:09,730
{\fnSimHei}我好奇... 什么使你成为曼丁哥专家的?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I'm curious... what makes you such a Mandingo expert?{\r}

830
01:09:11,690 --> 01:09:14,109
{\fnSimHei}我好奇是什么让你如此好奇{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I'm curious what makes you so curious.{\r}

831
01:09:17,404 --> 01:09:19,490
{\fnSimHei}- 你说什么 黑鬼?  - 布奇 冷静{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- What did you say, boy?  - Calm down, Butch.{\r}

832
01:09:20,533 --> 01:09:21,867
{\fnSimHei}他无意...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}No offense given...{\r}

833
01:09:22,701 --> 01:09:23,911
{\fnSimHei}也没有冒犯{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}none taken.{\r}

834
01:09:24,078 --> 01:09:25,788
{\fnSimHei}先生坎迪...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Monsieur Candie...{\r}

835
01:09:25,955 --> 01:09:29,458
{\fnSimHei}如果你能直接询问我的话 就再好不过了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I'd appreciate if you could direct your line of inquiry toward me.{\r}

836
01:09:29,625 --> 01:09:31,085
{\fnSimHei}第一...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}One...{\r}

837
01:09:31,710 --> 01:09:34,839
{\fnSimHei}你还没喝呢 能给你来点提神吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}you do not have anything to drink. Can I get you a tasty refreshment?{\r}

838
01:09:35,005 --> 01:09:37,842
{\fnSimHei}- 好的! 我要啤酒  - 极好的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Yes! I'll have a beer.  - Wunderbar.{\r}

839
01:09:38,008 --> 01:09:39,844
{\fnSimHei}罗斯科 给这位胡子先生一份啤酒{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Roscoe, a beer for the man with the beard,{\r}

840
01:09:40,010 --> 01:09:41,846
{\fnSimHei}我自己来个波利尼西亚珍珠潜水酒{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}and I will have a Polynesian Pearl Diver.{\r}

841
01:09:42,012 --> 01:09:44,098
{\fnSimHei}罗姆酒尽管放{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Do not spare the rum.{\r}

842
01:09:44,265 --> 01:09:47,768
{\fnSimHei}医生... 我是老练的奴隶贩{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Doc... I am a seasoned slaver.{\r}

843
01:09:47,935 --> 01:09:49,645
{\fnSimHei}你嘛 还是个新手{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You are, well, you are a neophyte.{\r}

844
01:09:49,812 --> 01:09:54,942
{\fnSimHei}我只是想确定 这牛仔是否在占你便宜{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I'm simply tryin' to ascertain if this cowboy here is takin' advantage of you.{\r}

845
01:09:56,402 --> 01:09:59,613
{\fnSimHei}恕我直言 先生坎迪...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}With all due respect, Monsieur Candie...{\r}

846
01:10:00,322 --> 01:10:02,199
{\fnSimHei}我不是来寻求你的意见的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I didn't seek you out for your advice.{\r}

847
01:10:02,366 --> 01:10:04,493
{\fnSimHei}我找你是要买个格斗黑人{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I sought you out to purchase a fighting nigger{\r}

848
01:10:04,660 --> 01:10:07,204
{\fnSimHei}市场上买不到的那种{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}at above top-dollar market price.{\r}

849
01:10:07,371 --> 01:10:09,915
{\fnSimHei}我印象中 当你让我作观众时{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Now I was under the impression, when you granted me an audience,{\r}

850
01:10:10,082 --> 01:10:12,459
{\fnSimHei}就是要讨论业务了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}it would be to discuss business.{\r}

851
01:10:15,170 --> 01:10:17,631
{\fnSimHei}哎 我们还没讨论生意呢{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Well, we weren't talkin' business yet.{\r}

852
01:10:17,798 --> 01:10:20,134
{\fnSimHei}我们刚才在讨论我的好奇{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}We were discussin' my curiosity.{\r}

853
01:10:22,428 --> 01:10:23,429
{\fnSimHei}谢谢{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Thank you.{\r}

854
01:10:23,596 --> 01:10:26,307
{\fnSimHei}罗斯科 可可 去外边玩{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Roscoe, Coco, go outside and play.{\r}

855
01:10:28,309 --> 01:10:31,770
{\fnSimHei}示巴... 你不用动{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Sheba... you stay right there.{\r}

856
01:10:31,937 --> 01:10:33,480
{\fnSimHei}我知道你指的不是我{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I know you didn't mean me.{\r}

857
01:10:35,232 --> 01:10:37,735
{\fnSimHei}- 干杯!  - 敬德国{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Prost!  - German.{\r}

858
01:10:38,652 --> 01:10:42,448
{\fnSimHei}根据莫吉说的 如果我和你做生意{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Now, according to Moguy, if I do business with you,{\r}

859
01:10:42,615 --> 01:10:44,658
{\fnSimHei}就是和你们俩都做生意{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I'm doing business with both y'all.{\r}

860
01:10:44,825 --> 01:10:47,244
{\fnSimHei}他打量 你掏钱? 是这样的吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}He does the eyeballin', you the billfold? Is that it?{\r}

861
01:10:47,411 --> 01:10:51,165
{\fnSimHei}嗯 别说的那么谄媚 但差不多是的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Well, you don't make it sound too flattering, but more or less, yeah.{\r}

862
01:10:51,332 --> 01:10:52,499
{\fnSimHei}嗯{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Hm.{\r}

863
01:10:53,792 --> 01:10:54,793
{\fnSimHei}那么...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}So...{\r}

864
01:10:54,960 --> 01:10:56,879
{\fnSimHei}机灵鬼...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Bright Boy...{\r}

865
01:10:57,046 --> 01:10:59,006
{\fnSimHei}莫吉说你看过我的非洲货了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Moguy tells me you looked over my African flesh{\r}

866
01:10:59,173 --> 01:11:01,342
{\fnSimHei}印象并不太深 是吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}and you was none too impressed, huh?{\r}

867
01:11:01,508 --> 01:11:03,010
{\fnSimHei}不是顶级好货{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Not for top dollar.{\r}

868
01:11:05,179 --> 01:11:07,222
{\fnSimHei}哦 既然这样 我们也没什么好谈的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Well, then, we got nothin' more to talk about.{\r}

869
01:11:07,389 --> 01:11:09,516
{\fnSimHei}看看 你想从我这里买黑人强手{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You see, you wanna buy a beat-ass nigger from me,{\r}

870
01:11:09,683 --> 01:11:11,936
{\fnSimHei}那些就是我想卖的高手 所以...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}those are the beat-ass niggers I wanna sell so...{\r}

871
01:11:12,102 --> 01:11:14,063
{\fnSimHei}他不想买你出售的黑人{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}He don't wanna buy the niggers you wanna sell.{\r}

872
01:11:15,022 --> 01:11:18,192
{\fnSimHei}他想买你不想卖的黑人{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}He wants the nigger you don't wanna sell.{\r}

873
01:11:18,359 --> 01:11:22,655
{\fnSimHei}喔 我不出售不想卖的黑鬼{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Well, I don't sell the niggers I don't wanna sell.{\r}

874
01:11:24,907 --> 01:11:28,577
{\fnSimHei}这个嘛 你不想卖最好的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Well, you won't sell your best.{\r}

875
01:11:28,744 --> 01:11:31,163
{\fnSimHei}也不会卖第二好的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You won't even sell your second best.{\r}

876
01:11:31,330 --> 01:11:35,000
{\fnSimHei}但第三好的...? 你还是不想卖{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}But your third best...? You don't want to sell him either.{\r}

877
01:11:35,167 --> 01:11:39,088
{\fnSimHei}但如果我出个惊天报价 你不得不考虑一下...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}But if I made you an offer so ridiculous you'd be forced to consider it...{\r}

878
01:11:39,880 --> 01:11:41,924
{\fnSimHei}谁知道会发生什么呢?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}who knows what could happen?{\r}

879
01:11:44,259 --> 01:11:46,553
{\fnSimHei}你觉得什么是惊天报价?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}And what do you consider ridiculous?{\r}

880
01:11:47,554 --> 01:11:51,642
{\fnSimHei}对一个有真正天赋的货色来说 那个对的人?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}For a truly talented specimen, the right nigger?{\r}

881
01:11:53,394 --> 01:11:55,437
{\fnSimHei}你觉得该出价多少 姜戈?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}How much would you say, Django?{\r}

882
01:11:58,816 --> 01:12:00,526
{\fnSimHei}一万二美金{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Twelve thousand dollars.{\r}

883
01:12:05,072 --> 01:12:09,076
{\fnSimHei}先生们 刚才我只对你们好奇{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Well, gentlemen, you had my curiosity,{\r}

884
01:12:09,243 --> 01:12:11,161
{\fnSimHei}但现在我注意到你们了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}but now you have my attention.{\r}

885
01:12:24,842 --> 01:12:30,514
{\fnSimHei}维利 维利 停车! 停车 啊!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Willie. Willie. Hold up! Hold up. Ah!{\r}

886
01:12:30,681 --> 01:12:33,100
{\fnSimHei}- 先生们早上好  - 舒尔茨医生早上好{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Good morning, gentlemen.  - Good Dr. Schultz.{\r}

887
01:12:33,267 --> 01:12:37,187
{\fnSimHei}- 今天真美啊 不是吗?  - 不能更美了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Beautiful morning, isn't it?  - You couldn't have picked a better one.{\r}

888
01:12:37,354 --> 01:12:40,232
{\fnSimHei}请跟我们一起乘维多利亚马车吧{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Please, won't you take a ride with us here in the Victoria.{\r}

889
01:12:40,399 --> 01:12:41,942
{\fnSimHei}噢 非常感谢{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Oh, thank you very much.{\r}

890
01:12:42,109 --> 01:12:44,236
{\fnSimHei}你可以把马栓到那边{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You can tie your horse up back there.{\r}

891
01:12:52,453 --> 01:12:53,746
{\fnSimHei}姜戈{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Django.{\r}

892
01:12:58,542 --> 01:13:02,171
{\fnSimHei}我与我的骨相学同事们不同的一点就是{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Where I part company from many of my phrenologist colleagues{\r}

893
01:13:02,337 --> 01:13:07,509
{\fnSimHei}我相信黑鬼能达到超乎聪明 超乎天赋{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}is I believe there is a level above bright, above talented,{\r}

894
01:13:07,676 --> 01:13:11,805
{\fnSimHei}超乎忠诚的水准{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}above loyal that a nigger can aspire to.{\r}

895
01:13:11,972 --> 01:13:16,643
{\fnSimHei}也就是 一个万里挑一的黑鬼{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Say, one nigger that just pops up in 10,000.{\r}

896
01:13:16,810 --> 01:13:18,312
{\fnSimHei}一个杰出的黑人{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}The exceptional nigger.{\r}

897
01:13:19,313 --> 01:13:21,356
{\fnSimHei}天气不错啊 是不是 机灵鬼?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Bright day, huh, Bright Boy?{\r}

898
01:13:22,483 --> 01:13:23,650
{\fnSimHei}太阳升起来了{\r}
