{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I want to be able to bill him as The Black Hercules.{\r}

1234
01:42:32,815 --> 01:42:34,191
{\fnSimHei}黑人大力神 这都被你想到了?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}The Black Hercules, isn't that clever?{\r}

1235
01:42:34,358 --> 01:42:35,359
{\fnSimHei}黑鬼大力神还差不多{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}More like Nigger-les.{\r}

1236
01:42:37,820 --> 01:42:43,200
{\fnSimHei}我说过 "我愿意花最高价{\r}
