1239
01:42:51,124 --> 01:42:53,836
{\fnSimHei}但他真的无可挑剔吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}But is he right as rain?{\r}

1240
01:42:55,087 --> 01:42:56,505
{\fnSimHei}舒尔茨医生{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Oh, Dr. Schultz,{\r}

1241
01:42:56,672 --> 01:43:00,467
{\fnSimHei}你得知道 在黑鬼搏击游戏中{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I will have you know there is no one in the nigger fight game{\r}

1242
01:43:00,634 --> 01:43:02,553
