{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}that appreciates the value of showmanship{\r}

1243
01:43:02,719 --> 01:43:04,471
{\fnSimHei}非鄙人卡尔文・坎迪莫属{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}more than Monsieur Calvin J. Candie here.{\r}

1244
01:43:04,638 --> 01:43:05,639
{\fnSimHei}非我主人莫属{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Nobody.{\r}

1245
01:43:05,806 --> 01:43:07,641
{\fnSimHei}但我们不能忘了黑鬼搏击游戏中{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}But one must not forget the most important thing{\r}

1246
01:43:07,808 --> 01:43:09,184
{\fnSimHei}最重要的一点{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}in the nigger fight game.{\r}

1247
01:43:09,351 --> 01:43:11,353
{\fnSimHei}他必须能打赢比赛{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}And that is a nigger that can win fights.{\r}

1248
01:43:12,896 --> 01:43:17,109
{\fnSimHei}你首要考虑的是赢 接着考虑的还是赢 赢赢赢{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Now that should be your first, second, third, fourth, and fifth concern.{\r}

1249
01:43:17,276 --> 01:43:19,319
{\fnSimHei}你要先确定他能打赢{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Now, after you have that, and you know you have that,{\r}

1250
01:43:19,486 --> 01:43:23,448
{\fnSimHei}再去加这些噱头{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}then you can start to implement a grand design.{\r}

1251
01:43:23,615 --> 01:43:26,159
{\fnSimHei}换句话说 打赢才是硬道理{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}In other words, first thing is first.{\r}

1252
01:43:26,326 --> 01:43:27,786
{\fnSimHei}打赢才是硬道理{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}First thing's first.{\r}

1253
01:43:35,460 --> 01:43:38,839
{\fnSimHei}你们很合得来嘛{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Ooh! I see you two getting on.{\r}

1254
01:43:39,006 --> 01:43:40,883
{\fnSimHei}非常合得来{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Famously.{\r}

1255
01:43:41,633 --> 01:43:44,303
