{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Oh, Monsieur Candie, you can't imagine what it's like{\r}

1256
01:43:44,469 --> 01:43:47,806
{\fnSimHei}你无法想像这有多么难受{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}not to hear your native tongue in four years.{\r}

1257
01:43:47,973 --> 01:43:49,808
{\fnSimHei}在波士顿(美国北方城市)待两个星期我都受不了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Well, hell, I can't imagine two weeks in Boston.{\r}

1258
01:43:52,227 --> 01:43:54,271
{\fnSimHei}在波士顿待两个星期!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Two weeks in Boston!{\r}

1259
01:43:54,438 --> 01:43:57,232
{\fnSimHei}坎迪先生 你真幽默!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Monsieur Candie, you a mess!{\r}

1260
01:43:57,399 --> 01:43:59,109
{\fnSimHei}在波士顿待两个星期!{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Two weeks in Boston!{\r}

1261
01:43:59,276 --> 01:44:04,489
{\fnSimHei}能用母语交谈真开心{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I can't express the joy I felt conversing in my mother tongue.{\r}

1262
01:44:04,656 --> 01:44:08,744
{\fnSimHei}希尔迪又是个口齿伶俐的姑娘{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}And Hildi is a charming conversation companion.{\r}

1263
01:44:08,911 --> 01:44:10,787
{\fnSimHei}当心点 舒尔茨医生{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Well, be careful now, Dr. Schultz.{\r}

1264
01:44:10,954 --> 01:44:13,707
