{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Nigger love's a powerful emotion, boy.{\r}

1266
01:44:16,126 --> 01:44:18,128
{\fnSimHei}就像一池子黑焦油{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}It's like a pool of black tar.{\r}

1267
01:44:18,295 --> 01:44:19,922
{\fnSimHei}陷进去就出不来了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Once it catches your ass, you're caught.{\r}

1268
01:44:20,088 --> 01:44:23,050
{\fnSimHei}没错 先生 无法自拔{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Yes, sir, you stuck.{\r}

1269
01:44:23,216 --> 01:44:24,760
{\fnSimHei}不知道呢 医生{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I don't know, doctor.{\r}

1270
01:44:24,927 --> 01:44:27,179
{\fnSimHei}你可以用德语对她说各种各样的甜言蜜语{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You can lay on all the German sweet talk you want,{\r}

1271
01:44:27,346 --> 01:44:31,850
{\fnSimHei}但这小妞貌似对姜戈很有兴趣{\r}
