{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}not the plucked chicken.{\r}

1275
01:44:43,654 --> 01:44:46,156
{\fnSimHei}舒尔茨医生 不需如此自贬{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Dr. Schultz, don't be so down on yourself.{\r}

1276
01:44:46,323 --> 01:44:48,241
{\fnSimHei}你可是一名有为的欧洲绅士{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You are quite the dapper European gentleman.{\r}

1277
01:44:48,408 --> 01:44:49,451
{\fnSimHei}要把盘子洗干净{\r}
