1278
01:44:49,618 --> 01:44:51,620
{\fnSimHei}就得用胳膊肘去洗 听见了吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}you got to put your elbow in these dishes, you hear me?{\r}

1279
01:44:51,787 --> 01:44:53,997
{\fnSimHei}你认识那个黑鬼吧?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You know that nigger, don't you?{\r}

1280
01:44:54,915 --> 01:44:56,208
{\fnSimHei}- 哪个?  - "哪个?"{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Who?  - "Who?"{\r}

1281
01:44:56,375 --> 01:44:59,461
{\fnSimHei}别跟我装傻 小贱人 你知道我说的是哪个{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Don't "who" me, bitch. You know who I'm talking about.{\r}

1282
01:45:01,213 --> 01:45:03,215
{\fnSimHei}坐在餐桌上那个?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}At the table?{\r}

1283
01:45:03,382 --> 01:45:04,633
{\fnSimHei}我不认识他{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I don't know him.{\r}

1284
01:45:04,800 --> 01:45:07,844
{\fnSimHei}- 你不认识他  - 不认识{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- You don't know him.  - No.{\r}

1285
01:45:08,011 --> 01:45:10,847
{\fnSimHei}- 礼貌点  - 不认识 先生{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- "No," what?  - No, sir.{\r}

1286
01:45:15,477 --> 01:45:17,938
{\fnSimHei}你不会跟我撒谎吧?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You wouldn't lie to me, now, would you?{\r}

1287
01:45:22,150 --> 01:45:23,360
{\fnSimHei}好{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}OK.{\r}

1288
01:45:24,611 --> 01:45:27,739
{\fnSimHei}这是你说的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Yeah. If you say so.{\r}

1289
01:45:34,204 --> 01:45:37,624
{\fnSimHei}毋庸置疑 爱斯基摩・乔符合我们的要求{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Eskimo Joe's a quality nigger, no doubt about it.{\r}

1290
01:45:39,001 --> 01:45:44,172
{\fnSimHei}但如果是我来付钱 我不会花12000块去买他{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}But if it was my money, I wouldn't pay no $12,000 for him.{\r}

1291
01:45:44,339 --> 01:45:46,675
{\fnSimHei}你会花多少钱?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}What would your price be?{\r}

1292
01:45:46,842 --> 01:45:48,802
{\fnSimHei}如果我出手阔绰的话{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Well, if I was inclined to be generous,{\r}

1293
01:45:48,969 --> 01:45:52,431
{\fnSimHei}我不知道他为何值得我出大价钱...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}and I don't know why I would be inclined to be generous...{\r}

1294
01:45:53,390 --> 01:45:56,643
{\fnSimHei}也许会出九千吧{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}9,000. Maybe.{\r}

1295
01:45:57,894 --> 01:46:03,692
{\fnSimHei}舒尔茨医生 我还是重申一下这次谈判的由来吧{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Dr. Schultz, let me reclarify how this whole negotiation came about.{\r}

1296
01:46:03,859 --> 01:46:06,028
{\fnSimHei}要知道 并不是我找上你们要卖黑奴的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You see, it wasn't me who came to you to sell a nigger.{\r}

1297
01:46:06,194 --> 01:46:07,154
{\fnSimHei}确实不是{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Sure wasn't.{\r}

1298
01:46:07,320 --> 01:46:09,031
{\fnSimHei}是你主动来找我 说要买黑奴的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}It was you who approached me to buy one.{\r}

1299
01:46:09,197 --> 01:46:11,366
{\fnSimHei}- 的确如此  - 机灵鬼提出的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Sure was.  - Now, that $9,000 figure{\r}

1300
01:46:11,533 --> 01:46:13,952
{\fnSimHei}九千美元这个数字也还算公道{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Bright Boy's been bandyin' about, that ain't too far off from right.{\r}

1301
01:46:14,119 --> 01:46:15,746
{\fnSimHei}但如果我想以这个价钱卖了爱斯基摩・乔{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}And if I wanted to sell Eskimo Joe for that,{\r}

1302
01:46:15,912 --> 01:46:18,874
{\fnSimHei}- 那随时都可以卖出去  - 随时都行{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- I could do so any day of the week.  - Any day.{\r}

1303
01:46:19,041 --> 01:46:23,295
{\fnSimHei}但就如你在格林维尔所说的 医生... 我不想卖他{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}But, like you said in Greenville, doctor... I don't want to sell him.{\r}

1304
01:46:23,920 --> 01:46:27,924
{\fnSimHei}只不过是你出的一万两千美元的好价钱{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}It was only your ridiculous offer of $12,000{\r}

1305
01:46:28,091 --> 01:46:30,927
{\fnSimHei}- 才让我予以考虑的  - 没错{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- that made me even consider it.  - Hm-mm.{\r}

1306
01:46:39,102 --> 01:46:43,190
{\fnSimHei}要知道 先生坎迪 您这话的确很有说服力{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You know, Monsieur Candie, you do possess the power of persuasion.{\r}

1307
01:46:47,110 --> 01:46:49,529
{\fnSimHei}好吧 先生坎迪 成交{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Why not? Monsieur Candie, you have a deal.{\r}

1308
01:46:49,696 --> 01:46:53,033
{\fnSimHei}- 一万二 买爱斯基摩・乔  - 万岁 医生{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- Eskimo Joe, $12,000.  - Hooray, doctor.{\r}

1309
01:46:53,200 --> 01:46:55,327
{\fnSimHei}万岁 真是明智的决断{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Hooray. And a wise decision that is.{\r}

1310
01:46:55,494 --> 01:46:59,039
{\fnSimHei}然而 这是很大一笔巨款{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}However, that is a tremendous amount of money.{\r}

1311
01:46:59,206 --> 01:47:02,375
{\fnSimHei}就像你有莫吉先生一样 我也有律师{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}And the way you have your Mr. Moguy, I have a lawyer.{\r}

1312
01:47:02,542 --> 01:47:04,336
{\fnSimHei}一个叫塔托的挑剔鬼{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Persnickety man named Tuttle.{\r}

1313
01:47:04,503 --> 01:47:07,589
{\fnSimHei}所以在我安心与你一手交钱一手交货之前{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}And I would need my Mr. Tuttle to draw up a legal contract{\r}

1314
01:47:07,756 --> 01:47:10,801
{\fnSimHei}我得让塔托先生起草一份合法的合同{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}before I'd feel comfortable exchanging that amount of money for flesh.{\r}

1315
01:47:10,967 --> 01:47:11,968
{\fnSimHei}可以{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Hm-mm.{\r}

1316
01:47:12,135 --> 01:47:13,804
{\fnSimHei}当然还得让我指定的医师{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Not to mention having Eskimo Joe examined{\r}

1317
01:47:13,970 --> 01:47:16,598
{\fnSimHei}- 给爱斯基摩・乔做个检查  - 这是自然{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- by a physician of my choosing.  - Naturally.{\r}

1318
01:47:16,765 --> 01:47:21,478
{\fnSimHei}这样一来 我大概...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}So, say I return in about...{\r}

1319
01:47:23,647 --> 01:47:25,941
{\fnSimHei}- 五天后回来  - 五天?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- five days time.  - Five days?{\r}

1320
01:47:26,108 --> 01:47:27,359
{\fnSimHei}和T塔托先生一起过来{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}With my Mr. Tuttle.{\r}

1321
01:47:27,526 --> 01:47:29,569
{\fnSimHei}然后就让我的塔托先生和你的莫吉先生{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}And then my Mr. Tuttle and your Mr. Moguy{\r}

1322
01:47:29,736 --> 01:47:32,697
{\fnSimHei}两个人把最后的细节都敲定{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}can hash out the finer details between themselves.{\r}

1323
01:47:33,532 --> 01:47:36,576
{\fnSimHei}我说这真是太棒了 医生 棒极了{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}I say splendid, doctor. Splendid.{\r}

1324
01:47:37,327 --> 01:47:38,495
{\fnSimHei}先生们...{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Gentlemen...{\r}

1325
01:47:39,496 --> 01:47:41,498
{\fnSimHei}我们来干一杯{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}may I propose a toast.{\r}

1326
01:47:43,875 --> 01:47:48,755
{\fnSimHei}敬爱斯基摩・乔 也许现在该称他为黑人大力神了吧?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}To Eskimo Joe. Or shall we call him The Black Hercules?{\r}

1327
01:47:48,922 --> 01:47:51,591
{\fnSimHei}敬黑人大力神{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}To The Black Hercules.{\r}

1328
01:47:51,758 --> 01:47:53,135
{\fnSimHei}敬黑人大力神{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}The Black Hercules.{\r}

1329
01:47:53,301 --> 01:47:54,719
{\fnSimHei}敬黑人大力神{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}To The Black Hercules.{\r}

1330
01:47:54,886 --> 01:47:58,723
{\fnSimHei}您说得对 医生 这名字的确响亮{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}You was right, doctor. That name do have pan-ass.{\r}

1331
01:47:58,890 --> 01:48:00,308
{\fnSimHei}真不错{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Hm.{\r}

1332
01:48:00,475 --> 01:48:03,728
{\fnSimHei}希尔迪 给我满上{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}Hildi, top my drink off.{\r}

1333
01:48:06,815 --> 01:48:11,862
{\fnSimHei}希尔迪 你喜欢在大宅子的晚宴上当侍从吗?{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}So, Hildi, how you like servin' at the big table in The Big House, huh?{\r}

1334
01:48:12,028 --> 01:48:15,240
{\fnSimHei}坎迪先生问你话呢 快点回答{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}When Monsieur Candie talk to you, you answers.{\r}

1335
01:48:15,407 --> 01:48:18,160
{\fnSimHei}- 我很喜欢 坎迪先生  - 是吧{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- I like it a lot, Monsieur Candie.  - Hm-mm.{\r}

1336
01:48:18,326 --> 01:48:21,079
{\fnSimHei}总好过在热箱子里关着 或是在布满荆棘的{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}It's a lot better than sizzlin' in that Hot Box or draggin' your ass{\r}

1337
01:48:21,246 --> 01:48:22,581
{\fnSimHei}灌木丛里奔跑{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}through a bramble bush.{\r}

1338
01:48:22,747 --> 01:48:25,834
{\fnSimHei}但也许却不如取悦那些曼丁哥来得有趣{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}But maybe it's not quite as much fun as gettin' to pleasure all them Mandingos,{\r}

1339
01:48:26,001 --> 01:48:27,586
{\fnSimHei}- 对吧 甜心?  - 天啊 她喜欢那些黑鬼{\r}
{\fnCalibri\fs14\b0}- huh, sugar bear?  - Oh, Lord, she like them niggers.{\r}

